<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0751c20shiWuEn"><lb
ed="T" n="0751c20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0751c20"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="beg0751sgsz10"/>宋<anchor xml:id="end0751sgsz10"/></date><placeName key="PL000000011478">杭州慈光院</placeName><persName key="A010035">晤恩</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0751c21"/><persName key="A010035">釋晤恩</persName>，字<persName key="A010035">修己</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000010157">姑蘇常熟</placeName>人也。姓路，母<persName key="A022516">張氏</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0751c22"/>甞夢<name>梵</name>僧入其家而妊焉。及稚孺，見沙門<lb
ed="T" n="0751c23"/>相，必起迎遲<ptr target="#n1280"/>。<date key="j20585442058909" from-iso="+0924-01-01" to-iso="+0924-12-31">年十三</date>，聞誦《彌陀經》，遂求出<lb
ed="T" n="0751c24"/>家。親黨饒愛，再三沮之，乃投<placeName key="PL000000010127">破山興福寺</placeName>受<lb
ed="T" n="0751c25"/>訓。<date notBefore-iso="+0930-03-28" key="j20608222062184" notAfter-iso="+0933-12-19">後唐長興中</date>受滿分戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g33"/>，登往<placeName key="PL000000010184">崑山慧聚<lb
ed="T" n="0751c26"/>寺</placeName>，學南山律。<date from-iso="+0936-11-22" key="j20632532063772" to-iso="+0938-04-25">晉<name>天福</name></date>初，從<placeName key="PL000000012746">檇李</placeName><persName key="A010003">皓端<roleName>師</roleName></persName>聽<lb
ed="T" n="0751c27"/>習經論，懸解<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1343"/>之性天然，時輩輒難抗敵。後<lb
ed="T" n="0751c28"/>微聞天台三觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>、六即<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1286"/>之說，冥符意解。<date notBefore-iso="+0944-02-02" key="j20658812067017" notAfter-iso="+0947-03-14">漢<name>開運</name><lb
ed="T" n="0751c29"/>中</date><ptr target="#n1281"/>，造<placeName key="PL000000011478">錢唐慈光院</placeName><persName key="A010039">志因師</persName>，講貫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>彌年<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1288"/>，通達《法<pb ed="T" n="0752a" xml:id="T50.2061.0752a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0752a01"/>華》、《光明經》、《止觀論》，咸洞玄微<ptr type="glossary" target="#g773"/>。尋施覆述，出<lb
ed="T" n="0752a02"/>弟子相次角立<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1287"/>。<date when-iso="+0986-09-12" key="j20814442081444"><name>雍熙</name>三年八月朔日</date>，<persName key="A010035">恩</persName>於中<lb
ed="T" n="0752a03"/>夜覩白光自井而出，明滅不恒，謂門人<lb
ed="T" n="0752a04"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010035">吾</ref>報齡極於此矣。」乃絕粒禁言，一心念<lb
ed="T" n="0752a05"/>佛。次夢擁納<ptr type="glossary" target="#g550"/>沙門執金罏焚香，三遶其室，<lb
ed="T" n="0752a06"/>自言：「祖師<persName key="A004896">灌頂</persName>來此相迎，<ref type="person" target="#A010035">汝</ref>當去矣。」夢覺，<lb
ed="T" n="0752a07"/>呼弟子至，猶聞異香。至<date key="j20814682081468" when-iso="+0986-10-06">二十五日</date>為弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0752a08"/>說「止觀」旨歸<ptr target="#n1282"/>及「觀心」義<ptr target="#n1283"/>。辰時，端坐面西而化，<lb
ed="T" n="0752a09"/>享年七十五，僧臘五十五。其夜院僧<persName key="A010040">有興</persName>、<persName key="A010041">文<lb
ed="T" n="0752a10"/>偃</persName><ptr target="#n1284"/>等皆聞空中絲竹嘹亮而無鞉鼓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1289"/>，且多<lb
ed="T" n="0752a11"/>鈴鐸，漸久漸遠，依<anchor xml:id="beg0752001"/>稀<anchor xml:id="end0752001"/>西去。迨<date key="j20814812081481" when-iso="+0986-10-19">九月九日</date>，依<lb
ed="T" n="0752a12"/><placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>法焚，獲舍利青白圓粒無算<ptr target="#n1285"/>。<persName key="A010035">恩</persName>平時<lb
ed="T" n="0752a13"/>謹重，一食不離衣鉢，不畜財寶，臥必右脇，<lb
ed="T" n="0752a14"/>坐必加趺。弟子輩設堂居，亦同今之禪室。<lb
ed="T" n="0752a15"/>立制嚴峻，日別親視明相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1290"/>，方許淨人施粥，曾<lb
ed="T" n="0752a16"/>有晚飲薯<anchor xml:id="beg0752002"/>蕷<anchor xml:id="end0752002"/>湯者，即時擯出黌堂。每一<lb
ed="T" n="0752a17"/>布薩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1291"/>，則澘洒不止，蓋思其《大集》「滿」「洲」之言<ptr target="#n1286"/><lb
ed="T" n="0752a18"/>耳。偏誨人以<persName key="A002843">彌陀</persName>淨業救生死事，受教得<lb
ed="T" n="0752a19"/>生感祥可見者，往往有之。凡與人言，不問<lb
ed="T" n="0752a20"/>賢、不肖，悉示以一乘圓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1295"/>意。或怪不逗機<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1292"/>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0752a21"/>乃曰：「與作毒鼓之緣耳<ptr target="#n1287"/>。」不喜雜交游，<lb
ed="T" n="0752a22"/>不好言世俗事。雖大人豪族，未甞輒問名<lb
ed="T" n="0752a23"/>居，況迂趨其門乎？先是天台宗教，<date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>毀<lb
ed="T" n="0752a24"/>廢，文義殘缺。談妙之辭，沒名不顯。<persName key="A010035">恩</persName>尋繹<lb
ed="T" n="0752a25"/>十妙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1293"/>之始終，研覈五重<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1294"/>之旨趣。講《大玄義》、《文<lb
ed="T" n="0752a26"/>句》、《止觀》二十餘周，解、行兼明，目、足<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1181"/>雙運。使《法<lb
ed="T" n="0752a27"/>華》大旨全美流于代者，<persName key="A010035">恩</persName>之力也。又慊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g543"/>昔<lb
ed="T" n="0752a28"/>人《科節》<ptr target="#n1288"/>與<persName key="A001307">荊溪</persName>記不相符順，因著《玄義》、《文<lb
ed="T" n="0752a29"/>句》、《止觀》、《金光明》、《金<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>[鏍-糸+廾]</sic><corr>錍</corr></choice>論科》，總三十五帖，見行<pb ed="T" n="0752b" xml:id="T50.2061.0752b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0752b01"/>於世<ptr target="#n1289"/>。吁，<placeName key="PL000000000193">河</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000026396">漢</placeName>中有魚泝流而上者何？潛泳<lb
ed="T" n="0752b02"/>有所取故。<persName key="A010035">恩<roleName>公</roleName></persName>不寬乘戒而出弟子十有<lb
ed="T" n="0752b03"/>七人，求解而行行耳。</p>
